      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoIs selected for comparison must be directly relevant to the clinical and regulatory decision being supported.",
      "rationale": "Construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement are the three QoIs specified in ASTM F1717 and directly relevant to the FDA regulatory submission for a pedicle screw system. These QoIs are clinically meaningful indicators of construct integrity under physiological loading."
